=== 蘭斯基事件 ===
2008年6月9日，《[[新科學家|新科學家]]》撰文介紹了[[生物學家|生物學家]]{{tsl|en|Richard Lenski|理查·蘭斯基}}的[[大腸桿菌|大腸桿菌]]長期演化實驗，其中的大腸桿菌在經過20年後[[進化|進化]]出了代謝[[檸檬酸鹽|檸檬酸鹽]]的能力<ref name="newscientist evolution research">{{cite web |first=Bob |last=Holmes |url=http://www.newscientist.com/channel/life/dn14094-bacteria-make-major-evolutionary-shift-in-the-lab.html |title=Bacteria makes major evolutionary shift in the lab |publisher=New Scientist |date=2008-06-09 |accessdate=2008-06-27 |archive-date=2008-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081009155106/http://www.newscientist.com/channel/life/dn14094-bacteria-make-major-evolutionary-shift-in-the-lab.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於此實驗對[[進化論|進化論]]是一處有利證據，夏拉伏雷對此持懷疑態度並聯絡蘭斯基要求檢視實驗數據。在蘭斯基回信指出實驗論文中已包括全部數據後，夏拉伏雷又要求檢視「原數據」。因此，蘭斯基發信指出其論文中確實已包括全部實驗數據、所謂「原數據」只能是指他實驗中的大腸桿菌樣品，他將願意給任何具備條件處理大腸桿菌的實驗者共享樣品、並且抗議夏拉伏雷敵視並毀謗他的實驗<ref>{{cite web |first=Michael |last=Marshall |url=http://www.newscientist.com/blog/shortsharpscience/2008/06/creationist-critics-get-their.html?DCMP=ILC-rhts&nsref=ts11_bar |title=Creationist critics get their comeuppance |publisher=newscientist |date=2008-06-25 |accessdate=2008-06-27 |archive-date=2009-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090111081024/http://www.newscientist.com/blog/shortsharpscience/2008/06/creationist-critics-get-their.html?DCMP=ILC-rhts&nsref=ts11_bar |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》認為蘭斯基的回覆是「史上最為有力而完善的科學辯述之一」<ref>{{cite web |first=Tom |last=Chivers |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/6408927/Internet-rules-and-laws-the-top-10-from-Godwin-to-Poe.html |title=Internet rules and laws: the top 10, from Godwin to Poe |publisher=telegraph |date=2009-10-23 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2018-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619173322/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/6408927/Internet-rules-and-laws-the-top-10-from-Godwin-to-Poe.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 保守百科對各類學說的批判 ==

=== 對演化論的批判 ===
保守百科認為，演化論是一門基於[[自然主義|自然主義]]的[[偽科學|偽科學]]。<ref name="Atheist Pseduoscience">{{Cite web |url=https://www.conservapedia.com/List_of_atheist_and_agnostic_pseudosciences |title=List of atheist and agnostic pseudosciences, Conservapedia |access-date=2022-05-01 |archive-date=2022-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501071345/https://www.conservapedia.com/List_of_atheist_and_agnostic_pseudosciences }}</ref><ref >{{Cite web |url=https://www.conservapedia.com/Evolution |title=Evolution, Conservapedia |access-date=2022-05-01 |archive-date=2022-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220429142434/https://www.conservapedia.com/Evolution }}</ref>

=== 對宇宙大爆炸論的批判 ===
保守百科認為，[[宇宙大爆炸|宇宙大爆炸]]論是一門站不住腳的科學理論。<ref name="Atheist Pseduoscience" /><ref >{{Cite web |url=https://www.conservapedia.com/Big_Bang_theory#Scientific_Criticism |title=Big Bang Thoery, Conservapedia |access-date=2022-05-01 |archive-date=2022-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501074350/https://www.conservapedia.com/Big_Bang_theory#Scientific_Criticism }}</ref>

=== 對[[無神論|無神論]]的批判 ===
