]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_death |title=Atheism and death |access-date=2022-05-01 |archive-date=2022-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220502041715/https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_death }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_death_anxiety |title=Atheism and death anixety |access-date=2022-05-01 |archive-date=2022-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503055132/https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_death_anxiety }}</ref>而提出及信奉[[人體冷凍技術|人體冷凍技術]]等[[偽科學|偽科學]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_cryonics |title=Atheism and Cryonics |access-date=2022-05-01 |archive-date=2022-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501081356/https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_cryonics }}</ref>，並信奉[[超人類主義|超人類主義]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_transhumanism |title=Atheism and transhumanism |access-date=2022-05-01 |archive-date=2022-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501091408/https://www.conservapedia.com/Atheism_and_transhumanism }}</ref>

